{"tid":1123053,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都好enjoy做deadline fighter","createTime":"2019-04-24T08:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T09:38:03.000Z","uid":205098,"like":71,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"dc148e72483883fc479381b1c29929636c56929f","tid":1123053,"uid":205098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T08:57:26.000Z","msg":"話說小弟我有個習慣 就係無論做乜嘢都一定要拖延到deadline前嘅最後一刻先開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盡情享受呢種唔知趕唔趕到deadline嘅焦慮感同內心深處對自己嘅責備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而呢種遊走係死亡邊緣嘅快感真係冇辦法好簡單咁用三言兩語黎描述 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知有冇同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9c656b75c88d3bebd815086256420ed486d5a2","tid":1123053,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T08:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296e7c20c3b38c1aa063231cde09357dcf698619","tid":1123053,"uid":205098,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:02:13.000Z","msg":"未試過做deadline fighter嘅人都可以去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5bd19e121d26903d132b01c8a427406d79354f3","tid":1123053,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:05:54.000Z","msg":"Edging 既快感，非筆墨所能形容"},{"pid":"240bc62716a6e1196e25470f4cc31627c4a95574","tid":1123053,"uid":205098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5bd19e121d26903d132b01c8a427406d79354f3","tid":1123053,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:05:54.000Z","msg":"Edging 既快感，非筆墨所能形容"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:12:16.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defdf790f140d5f4e08442181c885a95af1687fd","tid":1123053,"uid":205098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep